OL,5,G2300 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,6,     FWhen Bea learns she will be going
OL,7,     Fback to Wentworth soon, she drugs
OL,8,     Fher police guard and escapes from
OL,9,     Fthe hospital. Noeline continues to
OL,10,     Fthrow her weight around with Bea
OL,11,     Fabsent.
OL,12,G0000 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,13,     FMeg is suspicious when she finds a
OL,14,     Fpack of Bea's cigarettes. Jean has
OL,15,     Fto tell Lynn she has been fired,
OL,16,     Fbut Jean tries to talk Syd into
OL,17,     Ftaking her back. Noeline sets out
OL,18,     Fto bully Clara.
